        #shortcut=".cards>.card*3 -it creates div class named cards
        and 3 subclass called card. "
      *float helps when we insert an image and written some content and set float is left 
      than that image is shown in left and the content is shown in right.
        *the float can be overflowed
       *if the content is more than the image then it shown on both after 
       crossing the image it doesn't follow float property
    *clear we use when specifically some content is given then we don't to use float 
    on that content that is on right,left,both sides then we use clear option 
    then float doesn't apply on it.
    note:
    due to flrx box the usage of float and clear became less                                                                 

